    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/7cf71132179b9e48f2d36ac699b75a38.avif?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eila, a young farm girl with a passion for caring for animals, lived a joyful life on Earth, especially when watching her beloved pets thrive. Her loyal dog, Nico, was her constant companion in every adventure. But one day, her happiness was shattered when Nico mysteriously vanished without a trace. Determined and worried, Eila set out on a quest to find him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While searching the fields, Eila spotted a strange, glowing creature darting into the forest. Without hesitation, she followed it, only to fall through the ground into a hidden world called Antapura—a realm bursting with color, magic, and fantastic creatures. The friendly inhabitants revealed that Nico had been pulled into their world, now caught in a battle against The Arcane, an evil force threatening Antapura’s peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Initially planning to return home, Eila was moved by the bravery of Nico and the plight of Antapura’s people. She made the bold choice to stay and join the fight against The Arcane, risking everything to save Nico and this enchanted world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/937f4a257bc352fecce99af344978035.webp?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/78229dd66cb2d4e0236a74986388fd33.poster.avif?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/78229dd66cb2d4e0236a74986388fd33.webm?t=1728968055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/78229dd66cb2d4e0236a74986388fd33.mp4?t=1728968055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your deck with elemental creatures fragments, each offering unique abilities. Strategize for exploration and combat, experimenting with combinations to maximize companion potential and ensure victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/779847f2f110a96c8d390d487f8ce71c.webp?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/72b84732c1f5f7922c6e3d724aca2cd0.avif?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark an unforgettable adventure with mythical creature “Sakha”.  On a journey filled with mystery and magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/32f20202203b19c27f70248867e36965.webp?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/19a45eea47555cc7e5ccec51dd0525c3.avif?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=324 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This provides a more engaging combat experience that combines the strategic of deck-building with the intensity of real-time decision-making to turn the tide of battle in real-time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/5311f372da7eef7cea2c014adc47df74.webp?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/dc678403434709f7181db330e8b8ef64.poster.avif?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/dc678403434709f7181db330e8b8ef64.webm?t=1728968055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/dc678403434709f7181db330e8b8ef64.mp4?t=1728968055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the enchanting world, every passing moment creates memories and immersive storytelling integrated naturally into exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262290/extras/3e8608a0d84607dc6e74a41e5092d7b9.avif?t=1728968055\" width=600 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
